{"ts": "2026-06-07T20:23:39.839034+00:00", "update": {"tools": {"messages": [{"type": "tool", "data": {"content": [{"type": "text", "text": "successfully downloaded text file (SHA: 85bcd17c1bfa3c3b6179c895760d3aa82499a35f)", "id": "lc_2834816d-7dd2-40d2-b5a1-4cae05d4e6a4"}, {"type": "text", "text": "#!/bin/bash\n# Yes, I know this is bad. It uses a custom chunk-based file fingerprinter,\n# but it's not ready just yet and has shortcomings that have to be patched\n# by this bash script. I'm working on it.\nrm -rf build\nwebdev build\ncd build/images && mv * ../ && cd ../\n\ndart ../../../fingerprint/bin/fingerprint.dart\n\nfor i in $(find . -type f | egrep '\\.(svg|png|jpeg|jpg)$'); do\n    mv \"$i\" ./images/$i\ndone\n\ncd ../\n# firebase deploy", "id": "lc_d4813e9b-6234-4f67-a65c-9bd27ec2005a"}], "additional_kwargs": {}, "response_metadata": {}, "type": "tool", "name": "get_file_contents", "id": "90089704-b8b5-463e-97d1-257cda7bf947", "tool_call_id": "call_d1891ed76495414c8307bafd", "artifact": null, "status": "success"}}]}}}
{"ts": "2026-06-07T20:24:00.592759+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "Now I have a clear picture of this project. Here's an important note before giving you the commands:\n\n---\n\n## ⚠️ This is **not** a Flutter web project\n\nThis repo (inKino) is a **multiplatform Dart project**. The `web/` subfolder is an **AngularDart** progressive web app — not a Flutter app. The README states explicitly:\n\n> *The customized Dart version Flutter ships with is not suitable for web development.*\n\nBecause it uses AngularDart + `webdev`, the release build lands in **`web/build/`**, not `build/web/` (which is Flutter's output convention).\n\n---\n\n## Exact shell commands\n\n### (a) Install web tooling\n\n```bash\n# 1. Install the standalone Dart SDK (not the Flutter-bundled one)\n#    Follow: https://dart.dev/get-dart\n#    On macOS (Homebrew):\nbrew tap dart/dart && brew install dart\n\n# 2. Install the webdev build tool globally\npub global activate webdev\n```\n\n### (b) Fetch dependencies for this project\n\n```bash\n# 3. Rename the missing TMDB config sample so the project compiles\ncd core/lib/src && mv tmdb_config.dart.sample tmdb_config.dart && cd ../../..\n\n# 4. Fetch packages for the shared core library\ncd core && pub get && cd ..\n\n# 5. Fetch packages for the web app\ncd web && pub get && cd ..\n```\n\n### (c) Produce a release web build\n\n```bash\n# 6. Build the AngularDart web app for release\n#    (the output directory is web/build/, not build/web/)\ncd web && webdev build --release --output build\n```\n\n---\n\n### Summary in one consolidated script\n\n```bash\n# --- (a) Install tooling ---\nbrew tap dart/dart && brew install dart        # or equivalent for your OS\npub global activate webdev\n\n# --- (b) Fetch dependencies ---\ncd core/lib/src && mv tmdb_config.dart.sample tmdb_config.dart && cd ../../..\ncd core && pub get && cd ..\ncd web && pub get && cd ..\n\n# --- (c) Release build ---\ncd web && webdev build --release --output build\n```\n\nThe compiled output will be at **`web/build/`** (relative to the repo root). If you specifically need it at `build/web/`, you could symlink or move it, but that's not the convention this project uses.", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 1116, "prompt_tokens": 7885, "total_tokens": 9001, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": 0, "reasoning_tokens": 592, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null, "image_tokens": 0}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": 0, "cached_tokens": 4992, "cache_write_tokens": 0, "video_tokens": 0}, "cost": 0, "is_byok": true, "cost_details": {"upstream_inference_cost": 0.0022473462, "upstream_inference_prompt_cost": 0.0012764262, "upstream_inference_completions_cost": 0.00097092}}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "xiaomi/mimo-v2.5-pro-20260422", "system_fingerprint": null, "id": "gen-1780863820-XssQIQyHzLytwWilibIv", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ea3c1-6043-75e2-beb8-5efd78810e39-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 7885, "output_tokens": 1116, "total_tokens": 9001, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 4992}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 592}}}}]}}}
